------------------------ How to Study K8s -------------------------

- There are 3 ways to learn the kubernetes.
1. Run kubernetes on your Local system (Minikube).
2. Run kubernetes on Cloud environment (AKS, EKS, GKE).
3. Run kubernetes on PlayGround (Killer coda, k8s playground).
4. Also can run the kubernetes on-premise but now this is not popular way (Kubeadm).

