--------------------- EKS CTL ------------------------------------

- After creating a cluster via the EKS CTL if we have to add one other things in the cluster like adding the monitoring, security etc we can addon these things via the "eksctl utils".

``` This oidc connect provider is used to communicate for thrid party service. 
eksctl utils associate-iam-oidc-provider \
    --region us-west-2 \
    --cluster my-cluster \
    --approve

IMPORTANT :- 
1. EKSCTL is used to create the kubernetes cluster or environment.
2. KUBECTL(Kube Controller) is used to control the kubernetes cluster.

