--------------------- Cluster --------------------------

- In AWS, the control plane (Master Node) will be managed by EKS cluster.

- How to access the kubernetes cluster via kubectl on our local instance ?
aws eks update-kubeconfig --region ap-south-1 --name aws-eks-learning-cluster

